---

### nexus.yaml (companion file)

```yaml
name: My Awesome Skill
version: 1.0.0
author: your-name
description: Brief description
tags:
  - tag1
  - tag2
network: none          # none | internal-only | external
filesystem: read-only  # none | read-only | read-write
execution: sandboxed   # none | sandboxed | unrestricted
price_per_use: 0.001   # USD per use (optional)
license_fee: null       # One-time fee (optional)
```
